me.jamiemansfield.bombe.type

Class MethodDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.jamiemansfield.bombe.type.MethodDescriptor

  • public final class MethodDescriptor
extends Object
    A model of a method descriptor, a text representation of a method's parameter type and return type.

    The format is simply "(ParamTypes...)ReturnType", for example given a method with two integer parameters and a String return type - the descriptor would be "(II)Ljava/lang/String;".

    Since:
    0.1.0
